title: MsgIono
description:
The ionospheric parameters which allow the "L1 only" or "L2 only" user to,
utilize the ionospheric model for computation of the ionospheric delay.,
Please see ICD-GPS-200 (Chapter 20.3.3.5.1.7) for more details.
